txt.en: Find and defeat Captain Shêndi Grey-eye
'You found it! So much gold! I'm sure the, uh, proper amount will see its way to Umbar's coffers. Let's get you back to Umbar Baharbêl!'
Captain Shêndi Grey-eye has arrived to claim the treasure cache as her own!
As you touch the coin, cursed spirits leap out from the chest!
There are reports of a great treasure buried on a seldom-traversed island. You've been tasked with retrieving the treasure to help the restoration of Umbar.
Find and collect the treasure cache
Corsairs have beaten you to the treasure! Defeat the Corsairs and claim the treasure cache for the free peoples of Umbar.
